From the little german I remember...

  Bezeichnuwg: kugelkopf (ball type hitch)
  Tye: KA Grobe:36 Baujehr: 1956 (Type: KA, Size: 36, Manufactured:
1956)
  Zul Anhangelast Dis 1100 kg (Tounge Weight: 1100kg)
  Prurzoichen:  H.524

The last line im not sure of, but I think it pertains to the metal used,
as I said, I don't remember too much german, so I could be wrong on some
of this.

Jonathan

