small data plate on it with the following:

      Westfalia-Werk Wiedenbruck
  Bezeichnuwg: kugelkopf
  Tye: KA Grobe:36 Baujehr: 1956
   Zul Anhangelast Dis 1100 kg
   Prurzoichen:  H.524

  I have no idea what this means except maybe 1100kg tongue weight. The
